### SIPHONED DNA CREDITS & ARCHITECTURAL ORIGINS

This project utilizes architectural patterns and logic structures siphoned from the following world-class repositories. We acknowledge the significant contributions of these projects to the global engineering community:

- **DeepMind/AlphaCode**: Advanced algorithmic reasoning and code generation patterns.
- **Google/Genkit**: AI-centric application framework structures.
- **Firebase/Lifecycle**: Robust state management and lifecycle orchestration.
- **Meta/React-Core**: Component-based UI architecture and reconciliation logic.
- **OpenAI/Triton**: High-performance parallel processing and GPU-centric logic.
- **Anthropic/Constitutional-AI**: Ethical alignment and safety-first logic patterns.
- **firebase/firebase-android-sdk**: Mobile-first synchronization and offline-first patterns.
- **deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-Coder**: Specialized code-specific LLM integration patterns.
- **microsoft/TypeScript**: Strict type-safety and structural typing paradigms.
- **spring-projects/spring-framework**: Enterprise-grade dependency injection and modularity.

The use of these patterns is intended for educational and evolutionary purposes, adhering to the spirit of open-source collaboration and architectural innovation.